@controls
@mode:random(tempo:60.0000,striated,randomize)
S -> A[/5] B C D E
A -> {C3 B3 E3 F3 G3}[shuffle]
B -> ![@seed:1] {C4 B4 E4 F4 G4}[shuffle]
C -> randomize {C4 B4 E4 F4 G4}[shuffle] {C5 B5 E5 F5 G5}[shuffle]
D -> ![@seed:1] {C5 B5 E5 F5 G5}[shuffle]
E -> {rndvel(50) vel(80) a a a a a b b b b b}